cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is about semantic segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a deep neural network architecture and uses adversarial learning, which suggests that it may belong to the sub-categories of machine learning and artificial intelligence, such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper focuses on urban scenes, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM).
